                    <h3>🛡️ Family-Safe Play</h3>
                    <p>No public exposure. No open DMs. Designed to be boring to predators and safe for the world.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="card">
                    <h3>🔐 Memory Vault</h3>
                    <p>Adult-controlled logs and transcripts. Backend-ready infrastructure for private governance.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="card">
                    <h3>🏛️ Institution Grade</h3>
                    <p>NASA / UN-ready posture. Audit-ready framing for agencies and regulators.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="pricing">
            <h2>Pricing Preview</h2>
            <p>Introductory advertising pricing for limited time.</p>
            <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-around; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 20px;">
                <div><strong>Family:</strong> $0-$9/mo</div>
                <div><strong>School:</strong> Custom</div>
                <div><strong>Institution:</strong> Custom</div>
            </div>
            <p style="font-size: 0.8rem; color: #666; margin-top: 20px;">
                Disclaimer: GNAIAAAC LLC reserves the right to increase fees based on infrastructure scaling.
